                                                                <ul>
                                                                    <li>
                                                                        <div class="inner-top">
                                                                            <span class="title">지원금 차액 청구 예상금액 <span class="sub-tx">(일할계산)</span></span>
                                                                            <span class="tx-cont">
                                                                                <span class="tx-bold vbl">{{installmentAgreement.gapDcCd}}{{installmentAgreement.gapDcAmt}}</span>원
                                                                            </span>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                        <div class="inner-row top-line">
                                                                            <ul>
                                                                                <li>
                                                                                    <span class="title">현재 지원금</span>
                                                                                    <span class="tx-cont">{{installmentAgreement.frDcAmt}}</span>
                                                                                </li>
                                                                                <li>
                                                                                    <span class="title">변경 후 지원금</span>
                                                                                    <span class="tx-cont">{{installmentAgreement.toDcAmt}}</span>
                                                                                </li>
                                                                                <li>
                                                                                    <span class="title">지원금 차액</span>
                                                                                    <span class="tx-cont">{{installmentAgreement.gapDcCd}}{{installmentAgreement.gapDcAmt}}</span>
                                                                                </li>
                                                                                <li>
                                                                                    <span class="title">사용기간/약정기간</span>
                                                                                    <span class="tx-cont">{{installmentAgreement.agrmtUseCnt}}일/{{installmentAgreement.agrmtDayCnt}}일</span>
                                                                                </li>
                                                                            </ul>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                </ul>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="cont-noti mt20">
                                                                <ul class="bullet-type">
                                                                    <li>고객님의 약정잔여기간(약정기간-사용기간)을 고려하여, 보조금 차액 정산 부과액 또는 환급액이 결정됩니다.</li>
                                                                    {{#if installmentAgreement.isPremTerm}}
                                                                    <li>{{{installmentAgreement.premTermMsg}}}</li>
                                                                    {{/if}}
                                                                </ul>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </li>
                                        {{/if}}
                                        {{#if stipulationInfo.isScrbStplAgree}}
                                            <li>
                                                <div class="checkbox type01 fe-checkbox_style" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false">
                                                    <!-- 체크 상태가 아닐 경우 .checked 클래스 삭제, aria-checked="false" -->
                                                    <input type="checkbox" name="checkbox" value=""
